sql: SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.club c JOIN user_profile.club_user cu on c.id = cu.club_id JOIN user_profile.removed_user u on cu.user_id = u.user_id WHERE cu.user_role = 'OWNER';
SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.club_application ca JOIN user_profile.removed_user u on ca.user_id = u.user_id;
SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.club_user cu WHERE cu.club_id NOT IN (SELECT id FROM user_profile.club) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM user_profile.removed_user u WHERE cu.user_id = u.user_id);
SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.club_user_volume cuv WHERE cuv.club_user_id NOT IN (SELECT id FROM user_profile.club_user);
SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.club_volume_level cvl WHERE cvl.club_id NOT IN (SELECT id FROM user_profile.club);
SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.contact WHERE EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM user_profile.removed_user u WHERE user_profile.contact.user_id = u.user_id OR user_profile.contact.friend_user_id = u.user_id );

SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.user_recent_interaction_record WHERE EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM user_profile.removed_user u WHERE user_profile.user_recent_interaction_record.user_id = u.user_id OR user_profile.user_recent_interaction_record.friend_user_id = u.user_id );
SELECT count(1) FROM user_profile.admin_operation_log_for_user a JOIN user_profile.removed_user u ON u.chainup_id = a.chainup_id;
